metadata.name: DayAway Founder's Key #1 of 500
metadata.description: The Founder's Key is the first NFT enabled membership and loyalty program of its kind unlocking access to luxury experiences and VIP benefits worldwide. DayAway partners with the most iconic and reputable hotel, travel, F&B, wellness and retail brands to deliver exclusive access, discounts, and incentives to our community of discerning guests who appreciate quality experiences.
